title: [FSX/P3D] Drzewiecki Design - New York Airports X KJFK Extract
description:
Another small offering from me.

Let me know if it's working guys

ScamN2



This product is an extract from our New York Airports X package.

 This product is compatible with Microsoft Flight Simulator X (FSX) and Lockheed Martin Prepar3D (P3D).

Installation
After downloading the installer simply execute it. The scenery will be automatically added to the Flight Simulator Scenery Library. We have provided a few possible install settings so users could choose them accordingly to their simulator performance. Feel free to switch between different options by running the installer again. Details about these settings are described in the installer
